commodities.util
Class PropertyManager

java.lang.Object
  commodities.util.PropertyManager
public class PropertyManager
extends Object

The PropertyManager centrally manages property files. The properties file manager.properties contains entries for each property file that includes the name of the property file and the location of that property file. To retrieve a property from on of the files, use the following:
PropertyManager.instance().getProperties(PROPERTIES_FILE).getProperty(PROPERTY)
